<p><strong>Bakery section</strong></p>
</td>
<td style="padding: 2px; border-color: #000000;">
<p>Check sell-by dates</p>
</td>
<td style="padding: 2px; border-color: #000000;">
<p>Change price labels</p>
</td>
<td style="padding: 2px; border-color: #000000;">
<p>Use {yellow} labels</p>
