<p><strong>Sushi takeaway counter</strong></p>
</td>
<td style="padding: 2px; border-color: #000000;">
<p>Re-stock with<strong> </strong>{plastic}<strong> </strong>boxes if needed</p>
</td>
<td style="padding: 2px; border-color: #000000;">
<p>Wipe preparation area and clean the sink</p>
</td>
<td style="padding: 2px; border-color: #000000;">
